      "description": "This E46 M3 is a purist\u2019s example featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six, equipped with individual throttle bodies for instantaneous transient response. The powertrain is mated to a Getrag 6-speed manual transmission and a variable M differential lock, ensuring optimal torque distribution. Mechanically sound, the dual-VANOS system has been overhauled, and the rear subframe has received structural reinforcement to mitigate common floor pan fatigue. The suspension retains its factory-spec MacPherson strut and multi-link geometry, providing the precise kinemetics and 50/50 weight distribution this chassis is renowned for. Recent maintenance includes a valve adjustment and high-pressure fuel system inspection, ensuring the S54 pulls cleanly to its 8,000 RPM redline. A mechanically honest driver\u2019s car for the serious collector.",
